<item>
            <title>[CXF-5530] Wrong error code for non existing client&apos;s</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-5530</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently when I use non existing client_id on call I get response:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Response Code: 400&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;{
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;error&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;invalid_request&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;error_description&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Client ID is invalid&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;error_uri&quot;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But by RFC it should be returned error=&lt;b&gt;invalid_client&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6749#section-5.2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6749#section-5.2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Error is generated in that method:&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.cxf.rs.security.oauth2.services.AccessTokenService.getClient(String)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
